  "detailed_description": "When Major Tom is kidnapped, it’s up to you and the crew to infiltrate a mysterious and ancient alien complex in order to rescue him.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe road is filled with puzzles and death traps, but with the help of your beautiful allies, you’ll be able to overcome any challenge!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDifferent endings depending on your choices.<br />\r\n4 beautiful companions to choose from.<br />\r\nDeadly traps and puzzle elements.<br />\r\nMore than 24 illustrated scenes.<br />\r\n4 different endings.<br />\r\nVisual novel set in a sci fi environment. The story is completely different depending on which companion you choose, so you should play again to see the whole story!",
